15
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:16,000
I still remember my mom.

16
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:22,000
She had to borrow money so that she could have enough 23 million Vietnam Dome for me

17
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:29,000
to pay my tuition fee when it was the candidate in the National Excellent Student Contest,

18
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:34,000
the subject of English, which was pretty expensive back then.

19
