25
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:18,000
And plus, you were very likely to get a job offer after graduation.

26
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:26,000
And that is the reason why my parents wanted me to study to that university because they wanted to feel reassured

27
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:29,000
