38
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:33,000
So, you know, after one night, that video went viral all over the internet.

39
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:43,000
And wow, after a few weeks later, I got an invitation to film the music video and write some parts to the song with the songwriter.

40
