00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:20,000
And now he made it.

47
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:23,000
And I was like, wow, that would be a lot of fun.

48
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:28,000
I think this would be a very big opportunity for me, my time to shine.

49
