You know, if I was trying to sell you a pen and you didn't buy it,

66
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:45,000
okay, I could blame the pen is not good.

67
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:50,000
But when the product is me, when is me appearing on the National TV

68
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:54,000
