I mean, you're still a student.

74
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:15,000
You don't have to work. You can fail. You can try.

75
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:18,000
I just wanted you to be healthy and happy every day.

76
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:23,000
And an inner voice in me right at that moment told my mom that,

77
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:28,000
oh, my home, no, mom, I still want to keep working

78
