89
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:08,000
And I quit. That means I don't have enough passion for it.

90
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:10,000
I like to do the job of a TV host.

91
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:14,000
And I know that I have strong willingness to face

92
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:20,000
