257
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:55,000
At the end of the day,

258
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:58,000
we as humans, we are allowed to make mistakes.

259
00:14:58,000 --> 00:15:01,000
We are allowed to laugh at ourselves.

260
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:03,000
We are allowed to do something wrong.

261
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:05,000
Just make mistakes.

262
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,000
It's not the end of the world.

263
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:09,000
Who on earth has not made a mistake?

264
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:10,000
Tell me a name.

265
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:12,000
Who? No one.

266
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:14,000
So it's okay to feel bad.

267
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:17,000
It's okay to feel down and heavy sometimes

268
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:20,000
because the cloud rains when it's heavy too.

269
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:24,000
So it's really okay. It's totally normal.

270
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:27,000
You don't have to try to become anyone else.

271
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,000
You just be you.

272
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:31,000
And being you, being authentic, being an individual,

273
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:32,000
is enough.

274
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:36,000
Because individuality makes diversity.

275
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:41,000
And individuality and diversity are two most precious things on this earth.

276
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:44,000
I know that some of you here,

277
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:46,000
every single one of you here,

278
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:48,000
is the only thing that you can do.

279
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:51,000
I know that some of you here,

280
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:54,000
every single one of you here,

281
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:57,000
every single one of you here,

282
00:15:57,000 --> 00:16:01,000
might be having some problems and pressure to deal with every single day.

283
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:04,000
Maybe with your friends, with your family, with your work,

284
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:07,000
with your study, with your love life.

285
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:12,000
And I just want to tell you that no matter who you are,

286
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:14,000
no matter where you come from,

287
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:16,000
you are the one and only.

288
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:20,000
And that's what makes you beautiful and special in your own ways.

289
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:23,000
And no matter what you are facing right now,

290
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:28,000
and I don't know no matter what the future hosts for you.

291
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:32,000
Please, never change yourself.

292
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:35,000
Love yourself, accept yourself,

293
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:37,000
and then transform yourself.

294
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:39,000
I really hope you have a great day today.

295
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,000
Thank you.

